title: Chess Mobile Pro v3.2 APK (Android)
description:
This is the PRO version of Chess Mobile, with MORE FEATURES and AdFREE. No network permission is needed!
Very strong A.I. in expert mode! Try to beat the CPU or play against a friend.
This game allows you to rotate the pieces in 2 player mode. You can use your mobile (or Tablet) like a real chessboard!

Features:
- 4 difficulty levels
- very responsive A.I.
- 7 different chess board colors
- 6 different Background selectable
- undo function
- Statistics
- Load and Save Chess matches
- completely AdFREE (no Internet Permission needed!)
- improved performance
- much more
